													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[SHOWING THE DAMAGE]\r\n\r\nThe submersible drives onward toward the collapsing Iron Throne, maneuvering its way through the debris. \r\n\r\nThe spotlight hits one of the upper levels in which civilian gnomes and humans can be seen inside a glass-walled holding cell, which is already damaged. The submarine pans downard, passing another cell in which Grand Duke Ranvegard can be seen (provided Gortash's coronation already happened). He is calm, despite the chaos, thanks to his tadpole.\r\n\r\n"
												}
											},
