													"value": "[SUBMERSIBLE FINDS IRON THRONE]\r\n\r\nThe party travels with the submersible to the underwater Iron Throne building. A lightbeam spotlights the water in front of the submersible, seeing nothing but murky water until the Iron Throne comes into view - a ruined, submerged multi-storey building, topped by new, domed construction. "
