				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Players use the submersible to travel to the Iron Throne submersed building. On the way, spectator guards meet them and trigger the explosives on the upper dome of the facility. With little time before the prison facilities collapse, the players dock with the station, aiming to save the prisoners before it's destroyed."
